1
00:00:07,745 --> 00:00:09,025
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:37,145 --> 00:01:40,385
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:46,145 --> 00:01:48,945
Tie Ying commands an elite squad
of covert warfare.

4
00:01:49,665 --> 00:01:51,065
Night raid on Wuyang Pass,

5
00:01:51,145 --> 00:01:52,385
fire on Panying Pass,

6
00:01:52,465 --> 00:01:53,625
and massacre at Qingshi Stronghold.

7
00:01:54,465 --> 00:01:55,905
They've never failed.

8
00:01:57,305 --> 00:01:59,425
I've heard about this squad.

9
00:01:59,945 --> 00:02:03,105
They always strike on dark, windy nights,

10
00:02:03,185 --> 00:02:04,665
slaying all who stand in their way.

11
00:02:05,385 --> 00:02:07,145
In that case,

12
00:02:07,745 --> 00:02:10,024
I don't think we're likely to win.

13
00:02:14,065 --> 00:02:14,905
Not really.

14
00:02:14,985 --> 00:02:19,545
This squad excels at night raids
because they have superb hearing.

15
00:02:20,305 --> 00:02:22,545
That's why they can move freely
in the darkness.

16
00:02:25,105 --> 00:02:26,745
There's a way.

17
00:02:26,825 --> 00:02:28,785
We can set traps in the bamboo forest

18
00:02:29,385 --> 00:02:30,385
and catch them off guard.

19
00:02:31,065 --> 00:02:32,865
Then we'll shoot them from the shadows.

20
00:02:33,985 --> 00:02:37,145
Then, we might stand a chance.

21
00:02:41,465 --> 00:02:43,465
The whistle is our code.

22
00:02:43,545 --> 00:02:44,425
You can use it

23
00:02:44,505 --> 00:02:47,025
to make our people to set traps for you.

24
00:02:47,105 --> 00:02:49,585
During the fight, use it to communicate.

25
00:02:51,145 --> 00:02:52,065
Thank you.

26
00:02:52,665 --> 00:02:53,905
Tie Ying is mine.

27
00:03:17,425 --> 00:03:19,185
Mere child's play.

28
00:05:05,745 --> 00:05:08,425
Jiu, when you kill, you have steady hands.

29
00:05:09,465 --> 00:05:10,905
But now, they shake.

30
00:05:13,345 --> 00:05:14,305
I failed to protect you.

31
00:05:15,185 --> 00:05:16,145
Don't mind.

32
00:05:16,745 --> 00:05:17,785
It matters to me.

33
00:05:20,345 --> 00:05:23,065
Before, it was an order.

34
00:05:24,345 --> 00:05:25,305
But now,

35
00:05:26,905 --> 00:05:27,825
it's my duty.

36
00:05:30,265 --> 00:05:31,105
And the future?

37
00:05:34,425 --> 00:05:35,385
In the future…

38
00:05:41,305 --> 00:05:42,345
We'll see.

39
00:05:47,585 --> 00:05:48,505
Whatever happens,

40
00:05:49,345 --> 00:05:50,865
I will protect you.

41
00:05:58,985 --> 00:05:59,825
Tie Ying retreated.

42
00:05:59,905 --> 00:06:01,465
Your father is safe now.

43
00:06:04,625 --> 00:06:05,785
Thank you, ma'am.

44
00:06:12,185 --> 00:06:13,385
You helped a lot.

45
00:06:13,465 --> 00:06:16,945
To protect me, you suffered heavy losses.

46
00:06:18,905 --> 00:06:20,345
I don't know

47
00:06:21,345 --> 00:06:22,665
how I can repay you.

48
00:06:23,945 --> 00:06:25,865
Since we promised to protect you,

49
00:06:25,945 --> 00:06:27,785
we will keep our word.

50
00:06:28,385 --> 00:06:29,345
Tie Ying retreated.

51
00:06:29,425 --> 00:06:32,145
But more troops will be sent from Xiaonan.

52
00:06:34,025 --> 00:06:35,505
You'd better leave soon.

53
00:06:37,025 --> 00:06:37,905
Wait.

54
00:06:42,185 --> 00:06:43,665
My father gave this to me.

55
00:06:44,185 --> 00:06:46,665
When this is all over
and I'm back in the Capital,

56
00:06:46,745 --> 00:06:50,105
you people can ask me for rewards
with this jade pendant.

57
00:06:50,185 --> 00:06:51,945
‎WAR ENDS

58
00:06:57,665 --> 00:06:58,505
All right.

59
00:07:09,385 --> 00:07:11,265
What a nice piece of jade.

60
00:07:20,065 --> 00:07:21,625
Come on. Take it.

61
00:07:29,625 --> 00:07:30,905
Eat some of this.

62
00:07:38,425 --> 00:07:39,665
Have you noticed

63
00:07:40,585 --> 00:07:43,105
the way she looks at you is a bit strange?

64
00:07:43,785 --> 00:07:44,825
She means no harm.

65
00:07:46,305 --> 00:07:47,505
But strange, indeed.

66
00:07:51,265 --> 00:07:53,545
I think Tie Ying has fled back to Xiaonan.

67
00:07:54,305 --> 00:07:56,105
Xiao Xun's men will come again.

68
00:07:56,185 --> 00:07:57,465
It's not wise to stay here long.

69
00:07:57,545 --> 00:07:58,665
Right.

70
00:07:59,425 --> 00:08:00,625
We'll leave soon.

71
00:08:06,905 --> 00:08:10,905
Ma'am, in that fight, we had three dead
and seven badly injured.

72
00:08:10,985 --> 00:08:13,185
Three traps east were ruined
and need to be reset.

73
00:08:14,065 --> 00:08:15,585
Have our men properly settled.

74
00:08:15,665 --> 00:08:17,585
Yes. I'm on it.

75
00:08:17,665 --> 00:08:18,545
Let's go.

76
00:08:28,345 --> 00:08:29,545
You're about to leave?

77
00:08:31,625 --> 00:08:33,425
Don't bother to say goodbye.

78
00:08:33,505 --> 00:08:34,664
And you have apologized.

79
00:08:35,264 --> 00:08:37,225
But I have one question.

80
00:08:38,625 --> 00:08:42,505
What exactly happened
during my father's suppression?

81
00:08:44,425 --> 00:08:45,625
I told you, didn't I?

82
00:08:45,705 --> 00:08:46,625
I doubt it.

83
00:08:47,145 --> 00:08:48,305
I want the truth.

84
00:08:49,625 --> 00:08:52,185
This stronghold
is totally my father's style.

85
00:08:53,185 --> 00:08:55,625
I don't believe
it was just a misunderstanding.

86
00:08:56,385 --> 00:08:59,545
In that case, why did Mu Mianhong

87
00:09:00,145 --> 00:09:01,945
jump off a cliff instead of explaining?

88
00:09:10,065 --> 00:09:11,305
If you don't tell me,

89
00:09:12,585 --> 00:09:15,345
I might as well go ask my father.

90
00:09:22,105 --> 00:09:23,585
Do you know your father well?

91
00:09:24,225 --> 00:09:25,185
What kind of man

92
00:09:27,865 --> 00:09:29,225
do you think he is?

93
00:09:37,585 --> 00:09:38,665
My father…

94
00:09:40,385 --> 00:09:41,905
He's the God of War of our state

95
00:09:43,345 --> 00:09:45,265
and an all-powerful frontier hero.

96
00:09:46,305 --> 00:09:47,665
People respect him

97
00:09:48,625 --> 00:09:49,465
and revere him.

98
00:09:49,545 --> 00:09:50,625
Does that include you?

99
00:09:57,225 --> 00:09:58,665
Do you like this kind of father?

100
00:10:02,065 --> 00:10:03,025
No?

101
00:10:04,545 --> 00:10:05,385
Why?

102
00:10:12,225 --> 00:10:13,985
Because he's a hero to others.

103
00:10:16,385 --> 00:10:18,465
He's a hero to people in Yunzhong.

104
00:10:19,225 --> 00:10:20,545
He's a hero to the State of Chu.

105
00:10:21,745 --> 00:10:25,065
But I want him to be an ordinary father.

106
00:10:25,665 --> 00:10:27,305
Carve wooden dolls for me,

107
00:10:28,145 --> 00:10:29,825
watch fireworks with me,

108
00:10:31,225 --> 00:10:33,225
give me pretty braids,

109
00:10:34,945 --> 00:10:38,385
and be there with me
for every important moment.

110
00:10:41,105 --> 00:10:42,265
But actually…

111
00:10:44,185 --> 00:10:45,425
none of this happened.

112
00:10:47,705 --> 00:10:48,665
What about…

113
00:10:51,945 --> 00:10:52,905
your mother?

114
00:10:53,505 --> 00:10:54,505
My mother?

115
00:11:00,825 --> 00:11:02,785
I guess she's a great lady.

116
00:11:03,705 --> 00:11:05,225
According to my father,

117
00:11:05,865 --> 00:11:08,145
she's a perfect woman.

118
00:11:08,745 --> 00:11:09,985
She was well-learned

119
00:11:10,585 --> 00:11:12,585
and versed in all arts.

120
00:11:15,225 --> 00:11:16,825
Sadly, I didn't witness that.

121
00:11:19,065 --> 00:11:20,505
My mother died at a young age.

122
00:11:22,185 --> 00:11:26,585
For as long as I can remember,
I have no memories of her.

123
00:11:27,945 --> 00:11:29,305
Sometimes I wish,

124
00:11:31,065 --> 00:11:32,985
if only my mother were alive.

125
00:11:33,585 --> 00:11:36,625
Then she would have stood up for me
when Father scolded me.

126
00:11:37,465 --> 00:11:39,385
She would do my hair nicely.

127
00:11:39,465 --> 00:11:42,665
When people laughed at me
for failing at everything,

128
00:11:44,305 --> 00:11:45,945
she would still treasure me

129
00:11:47,185 --> 00:11:48,785
and always protect me.

130
00:11:51,025 --> 00:11:52,505
But what a pity.

131
00:11:52,585 --> 00:11:53,865
My mother is gone.

132
00:11:54,785 --> 00:11:56,705
Sometimes, I blame myself.

133
00:11:58,185 --> 00:12:01,865
Why couldn't I remember everything
when I was born?

134
00:12:02,865 --> 00:12:04,105
In that case,

135
00:12:05,505 --> 00:12:07,865
I would know what my mother looked like.

136
00:12:12,705 --> 00:12:15,465
My father claimed he loved my mother.

137
00:12:16,265 --> 00:12:17,825
But throughout our mansion,

138
00:12:18,625 --> 00:12:20,105
in the past 19 years,

139
00:12:20,185 --> 00:12:22,665
there has never been
a single portrait of her.

140
00:12:24,745 --> 00:12:26,105
In your imagination,

141
00:12:28,265 --> 00:12:29,905
what does she look like?

142
00:12:33,265 --> 00:12:35,265
She's a noble lady,
according to my father.

143
00:12:36,785 --> 00:12:38,065
So she must have

144
00:12:38,945 --> 00:12:40,465
delicate eyebrows,

145
00:12:41,425 --> 00:12:42,865
bright eyes,

146
00:12:44,945 --> 00:12:46,585
and porcelain skin.

147
00:12:53,945 --> 00:12:54,945
Girl,

148
00:12:56,785 --> 00:12:58,505
whatever your mother looks like,

149
00:13:02,225 --> 00:13:03,505
your father loves you

150
00:13:04,705 --> 00:13:06,225
more than his own life.

151
00:13:08,065 --> 00:13:09,665
This has never changed.

152
00:13:20,145 --> 00:13:21,505
Zhao.

153
00:13:22,505 --> 00:13:24,185
How could you not know

154
00:13:24,265 --> 00:13:25,705
your letter

155
00:13:26,585 --> 00:13:30,785
would make him let down his guard?

156
00:13:31,865 --> 00:13:32,825
You're right.

157
00:13:38,105 --> 00:13:39,505
And that's enough.

158
00:13:51,585 --> 00:13:52,825
Your mother loves you too.

159
00:14:23,025 --> 00:14:25,145
Sorry, I failed.

160
00:14:25,225 --> 00:14:26,465
Please forgive me.

161
00:14:29,745 --> 00:14:30,785
Where are our men?

162
00:14:32,385 --> 00:14:33,505
The terrain there is eerie.

163
00:14:34,105 --> 00:14:35,665
Too many traps in the forest.

164
00:14:35,745 --> 00:14:38,625
We lost over half of our men.

165
00:14:40,745 --> 00:14:42,465
But I've figured out their defenses.

166
00:14:42,545 --> 00:14:43,665
I request another attack.

167
00:14:44,345 --> 00:14:47,145
Chu Zhao isn't stupid enough
to wait there to die.

168
00:14:47,785 --> 00:14:49,585
She's eager to go back to Yunzhong.

169
00:14:49,665 --> 00:14:51,505
She won't stay long there.

170
00:14:52,105 --> 00:14:55,465
She has to pass through Wangcheng
to get to Yunzhong.

171
00:14:56,065 --> 00:14:58,345
Since Cangmu Stronghold
is tough to invade,

172
00:15:00,385 --> 00:15:02,025
we'll be waiting for her further ahead.

173
00:15:03,025 --> 00:15:05,185
Cangmu Stronghold lies at a key junction.

174
00:15:05,265 --> 00:15:06,825
If Chu Ling incorporates them,

175
00:15:07,385 --> 00:15:09,025
he will be more formidable.

176
00:15:12,025 --> 00:15:13,065
Tie Ying,

177
00:15:14,145 --> 00:15:15,385
send word to the Northern Desert.

178
00:15:16,625 --> 00:15:20,785
Tell them I want another deal
with their king.

179
00:15:28,145 --> 00:15:30,145
Congratulations. You won again.

180
00:15:35,625 --> 00:15:36,505
Do you think

181
00:15:37,585 --> 00:15:40,785
Zhao will be in trouble?

182
00:15:41,385 --> 00:15:42,545
Don't worry. Your Majesty.

183
00:15:42,625 --> 00:15:44,625
Before Her Highness left,
I divined for her.

184
00:15:44,705 --> 00:15:47,745
During the trip,
she'll escape all misfortune.

185
00:15:49,905 --> 00:15:50,825
Your Majesty.

186
00:15:55,505 --> 00:15:57,705
Uncle, did you come so late

187
00:15:57,785 --> 00:16:00,225
because Zhao and Uncle Yanlai
were in some trouble?

188
00:16:01,825 --> 00:16:03,745
Yanlai is skilled in martial arts.

189
00:16:03,825 --> 00:16:05,265
He'll protect Zhao.

190
00:16:05,345 --> 00:16:06,665
Don't worry.

191
00:16:06,745 --> 00:16:08,425
General Chu Ling

192
00:16:08,505 --> 00:16:10,745
killed the envoy without permission.

193
00:16:11,265 --> 00:16:12,585
It might lead to trouble.

194
00:16:13,185 --> 00:16:14,785
His old illness relapsed too.

195
00:16:14,865 --> 00:16:16,345
He might not survive this winter.

196
00:16:17,345 --> 00:16:20,225
In the court, the Grand Mentor said,

197
00:16:20,825 --> 00:16:23,905
if General Chu died, war would break out.

198
00:16:24,505 --> 00:16:27,025
So, our frontier forces
should prepare early.

199
00:16:27,625 --> 00:16:28,585
Exactly.

200
00:16:29,505 --> 00:16:32,825
The 200,000 frontier troops in Yunzhong
safeguard our state.

201
00:16:33,425 --> 00:16:35,305
If Northern Desert foes invade…

202
00:16:35,385 --> 00:16:36,305
Yu,

203
00:16:37,305 --> 00:16:38,665
do you dare to fight in battle?

204
00:16:39,465 --> 00:16:40,985
I will fight.

205
00:16:41,505 --> 00:16:43,305
We people never fear a battle.

206
00:16:44,745 --> 00:16:45,665
Good.

207
00:16:46,185 --> 00:16:49,425
Let me ask you one more thing.

208
00:16:50,025 --> 00:16:51,185
If Chu Ling dies,

209
00:16:51,705 --> 00:16:55,705
who should command
the 200,000 frontier troops?

210
00:16:57,425 --> 00:16:59,465
Uncle Yanlai. He has great martial arts.

211
00:17:06,385 --> 00:17:07,305
Your Majesty,

212
00:17:07,385 --> 00:17:09,424
then get the edict ready.

213
00:17:09,505 --> 00:17:10,704
So we can plan ahead.

214
00:17:12,905 --> 00:17:14,025
Wait, Your Majesty.

215
00:17:18,944 --> 00:17:20,985
Mr. Xie, you're really impatient.

216
00:17:23,184 --> 00:17:26,665
Your Majesty,
military affairs are of vital importance

217
00:17:27,265 --> 00:17:28,385
and need court discussion.

218
00:17:29,225 --> 00:17:31,225
Mr. Xie shouldn't have incited you
in private.

219
00:17:31,305 --> 00:17:34,945
Mr. Deng,
are you trying to delay military action?

220
00:17:35,585 --> 00:17:36,945
I hold the Imperial Seal.

221
00:17:37,025 --> 00:17:39,945
Without the seal on it,
this edict will be invalid.

222
00:17:41,145 --> 00:17:43,145
The Three Departments
approve troop deployment.

223
00:17:43,745 --> 00:17:47,905
It's time for you to end
this practice of nepotism.

224
00:18:03,785 --> 00:18:06,465
‎MILITARY CAMP OF NORTHERN DESERT

225
00:18:14,705 --> 00:18:15,825
Word from Xiao Xun.

226
00:18:15,905 --> 00:18:17,225
Chu Ling is seriously sick.

227
00:18:17,305 --> 00:18:18,425
The Chu court is in chaos.

228
00:18:19,025 --> 00:18:21,425
He wants 3,000 elite soldiers of ours

229
00:18:21,505 --> 00:18:23,825
to bypass Xiaonan and go to Wangcheng

230
00:18:24,345 --> 00:18:26,185
to join the Xiaonan Army
in besieging Yunzhong.

231
00:18:26,265 --> 00:18:29,745
Then, we'll split his state.

232
00:18:31,465 --> 00:18:33,625
He's the most eager of all.

233
00:18:34,225 --> 00:18:36,225
After all these years as a hostage,

234
00:18:36,305 --> 00:18:39,025
he still hasn't become patient.

235
00:18:39,625 --> 00:18:41,425
Come on, Chu Ling.

236
00:18:42,825 --> 00:18:45,585
We've been fighting for two decades.

237
00:18:45,665 --> 00:18:48,825
The state you've guarded with your life

238
00:18:49,425 --> 00:18:51,625
corroded from within a long time ago.

239
00:18:57,465 --> 00:18:58,985
Their ministers scheme against each other.

240
00:18:59,065 --> 00:18:59,905
KING OF NORTHERN DESERT

241
00:18:59,985 --> 00:19:01,345
Even a hostage dares

242
00:19:03,025 --> 00:19:05,865
to collude with enemies for invasion.

243
00:19:09,985 --> 00:19:15,185
Now, it's our time to take over Yunzhong.

244
00:19:16,065 --> 00:19:18,625
But mountain defiles
are perilous in Xiaonan.

245
00:19:18,705 --> 00:19:20,225
Supplies can't get through.

246
00:19:20,825 --> 00:19:24,105
Wangcheng lies to the rear of Yunzhong.

247
00:19:25,705 --> 00:19:27,705
It's weakly guarded.

248
00:19:28,425 --> 00:19:31,825
We'll travel light for a night raid.

249
00:19:31,905 --> 00:19:34,225
Capturing it quickly won't be a problem.

250
00:19:39,305 --> 00:19:41,425
Go. Tell Xiao Xun.

251
00:19:41,505 --> 00:19:44,785
I will wait for him in Wangcheng.

252
00:19:49,985 --> 00:19:52,585
WANGCHENG

253
00:19:57,705 --> 00:20:01,265
Son, we need to think carefully.

254
00:20:02,865 --> 00:20:05,225
The Northern Desert King is treacherous.

255
00:20:05,305 --> 00:20:08,385
To work with him is to play with fire.

256
00:20:09,065 --> 00:20:11,185
He has probed me for years,

257
00:20:11,265 --> 00:20:12,425
but I've never agreed.

258
00:20:12,505 --> 00:20:15,465
If we work with him,
there may be unnecessary trouble.

259
00:20:17,385 --> 00:20:18,865
Can you guarantee

260
00:20:19,905 --> 00:20:22,145
that everything will be under control

261
00:20:22,225 --> 00:20:24,465
once his soldiers come in here?

262
00:20:26,625 --> 00:20:28,585
Without a perfect plan,

263
00:20:31,985 --> 00:20:33,625
we might as well wait.

264
00:20:34,945 --> 00:20:36,705
Father, I understand your concern.

265
00:20:37,425 --> 00:20:38,625
But in some cases,

266
00:20:39,945 --> 00:20:41,585
patience doesn't solve anything.

267
00:20:42,465 --> 00:20:44,945
I don't want to repeat the same mistakes.

268
00:20:46,745 --> 00:20:47,945
Chu Ling is badly ill.

269
00:20:48,785 --> 00:20:50,505
This is the perfect moment.

270
00:20:51,105 --> 00:20:52,425
We'll use our northern foes

271
00:20:53,305 --> 00:20:54,905
to support our own cause.

272
00:21:02,425 --> 00:21:03,945
I get it.

273
00:21:04,025 --> 00:21:06,145
Since you've made up your mind,

274
00:21:07,745 --> 00:21:08,625
go ahead and do it.

275
00:21:10,905 --> 00:21:12,225
Thank you, Father.

276
00:21:14,785 --> 00:21:17,865
I should send a few men to escort you.

277
00:21:19,145 --> 00:21:21,185
I've brought too much trouble to you.

278
00:21:21,265 --> 00:21:22,705
Many innocent people died.

279
00:21:23,585 --> 00:21:25,865
I will keep that in mind.

280
00:21:29,145 --> 00:21:30,265
You helped us at all costs.

281
00:21:30,865 --> 00:21:33,065
Whatever you want, just let me know.

282
00:21:34,345 --> 00:21:35,745
We want nothing from you.

283
00:21:36,825 --> 00:21:38,705
We just hope you won't forget us

284
00:21:38,785 --> 00:21:41,425
when you're back there
and grant us some rewards.

285
00:21:42,065 --> 00:21:43,145
I will.

286
00:21:45,105 --> 00:21:46,465
That jade piece…

287
00:21:46,545 --> 00:21:47,745
Please keep it for me.

288
00:21:48,465 --> 00:21:49,625
Sure.

289
00:21:50,345 --> 00:21:52,905
Cangmu Forest isn't far from Wangcheng.

290
00:21:52,985 --> 00:21:55,425
Xiaonan's killers may pursue you, though.

291
00:21:56,065 --> 00:21:57,705
Every half day, Wangcheng soldiers

292
00:21:57,785 --> 00:21:59,745
patrol the foot of the mountain.

293
00:22:00,665 --> 00:22:01,705
Be more careful out there.

294
00:22:03,265 --> 00:22:04,865
Thank you for reminding me.

295
00:22:04,945 --> 00:22:05,985
We know what to do.

296
00:22:07,265 --> 00:22:08,105
That's good.

297
00:22:13,105 --> 00:22:14,305
Take care.

298
00:22:18,425 --> 00:22:22,345
‎GATEWAY OF CANGMU STRONGHOLD

299
00:22:42,625 --> 00:22:44,985
IN HARMONY WITH YIN AND YANG

300
00:22:47,945 --> 00:22:50,945
You issued the transfer edict, right?

301
00:22:54,025 --> 00:22:56,465
Where did you get this?

302
00:22:56,985 --> 00:23:00,665
Theoretically,
this edict should have left the Capital.

303
00:23:01,385 --> 00:23:05,025
Intercepting an imperial edict
is a grave crime.

304
00:23:05,625 --> 00:23:06,745
I did intercept it.

305
00:23:11,705 --> 00:23:13,345
What does it mean?

306
00:23:17,545 --> 00:23:18,505
It means

307
00:23:19,065 --> 00:23:20,985
without my approval,

308
00:23:22,025 --> 00:23:23,785
it can't be issued.

309
00:23:23,865 --> 00:23:28,185
Do you think I can't hold you accountable
just because of who you are?

310
00:23:28,265 --> 00:23:29,585
You can do that.

311
00:23:30,505 --> 00:23:32,145
But I advise you not to do that.

312
00:23:32,785 --> 00:23:34,545
If we both lose in the end,

313
00:23:35,505 --> 00:23:36,865
our state will be in peril.

314
00:23:36,945 --> 00:23:40,025
Since you know that,
why don't you advise yourself?

315
00:23:40,625 --> 00:23:44,265
You don't fear the peril of the state.
Why would I be scared?

316
00:23:44,865 --> 00:23:47,905
So late at night, you visited
His Majesty and coaxed him.

317
00:23:47,985 --> 00:23:49,945
Why can't I ease his burdens?

318
00:23:50,025 --> 00:23:51,625
Of course, you aren't afraid.

319
00:23:52,225 --> 00:23:56,505
But the way you ease burdens
is a clear overreach of your authority.

320
00:23:57,465 --> 00:24:00,985
How dare you issue an edict
without His Majesty's decision?

321
00:24:01,785 --> 00:24:03,425
Do you also want

322
00:24:04,265 --> 00:24:05,945
to sit on the throne

323
00:24:06,545 --> 00:24:08,025
to ease His Majesty's burdens?

324
00:24:09,145 --> 00:24:11,585
You overestimate me, Mr. Xie.

325
00:24:12,145 --> 00:24:14,665
His Majesty is aware of all this.

326
00:24:15,425 --> 00:24:16,425
As for you…

327
00:24:16,505 --> 00:24:19,265
Do you really think
Chu Ling's defeat of an enemy army

328
00:24:19,345 --> 00:24:21,145
will bring peace?

329
00:24:22,105 --> 00:24:23,785
Once Chu Ling dies a sudden death,

330
00:24:23,865 --> 00:24:26,265
Yunzhong troops will fall into chaos.

331
00:24:26,785 --> 00:24:29,065
Then our state will be in real peril.

332
00:24:30,025 --> 00:24:31,105
Others might not know.

333
00:24:31,185 --> 00:24:32,505
But we both know

334
00:24:32,585 --> 00:24:36,545
what the Lord of Xiaonan will do
when Yunzhong is in chaos.

335
00:24:36,625 --> 00:24:38,705
What will the Lord of Xiaonan do?

336
00:24:40,905 --> 00:24:42,665
You know it perfectly well, don't you?

337
00:24:43,705 --> 00:24:46,865
Back then, you insisted
Xiao Xun return to Xiaonan.

338
00:24:47,465 --> 00:24:48,825
When the hostage left,

339
00:24:48,905 --> 00:24:50,745
you should have foreseen this day.

340
00:24:50,825 --> 00:24:52,385
Xie Yanfang!

341
00:24:53,505 --> 00:24:56,385
Your duty is merely to enforce edicts.

342
00:24:56,465 --> 00:24:58,585
You have no say in military affairs.

343
00:24:58,665 --> 00:25:00,225
This is a real overreach of authority!

344
00:25:01,865 --> 00:25:06,585
WISDOM AND VIRTUES

345
00:25:14,705 --> 00:25:16,545
Here's the Grand Princess Token.

346
00:25:17,585 --> 00:25:21,185
I'm exercising the veto power
on behalf of Her Highness.

347
00:25:26,465 --> 00:25:28,385
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

348
00:25:36,785 --> 00:25:37,625
Madam Ge said,

349
00:25:37,705 --> 00:25:40,305
Wangcheng soldiers patrol at this hour.

350
00:25:40,385 --> 00:25:41,705
She's right.

351
00:25:43,065 --> 00:25:46,825
So, what exactly is your great plan?

352
00:25:47,465 --> 00:25:48,825
We'll "surrender".

353
00:25:51,105 --> 00:25:55,345
Are you saying we'll deliberately
let these patrols catch us

354
00:25:55,425 --> 00:25:56,265
and take us to Wangcheng?

355
00:25:56,985 --> 00:26:00,385
So, Mr. Xie, show some mercy in the fight.

356
00:26:02,545 --> 00:26:03,465
Who are you?

357
00:26:05,905 --> 00:26:06,945
I don't think

358
00:26:07,945 --> 00:26:09,225
there'll be a fight.

359
00:26:13,265 --> 00:26:14,585
<i>It's him.</i>

360
00:26:19,225 --> 00:26:20,465
<i>In my past life,</i>

361
00:26:20,985 --> 00:26:23,425
<i>he was a vanguard</i>
<i>under my father's command.</i>

362
00:26:23,505 --> 00:26:25,745
<i>But now, he seems to be</i>

363
00:26:26,625 --> 00:26:29,385
<i>a foot soldier among Wangcheng troops.</i>

364
00:26:30,385 --> 00:26:31,225
Liang Qiang.

365
00:26:35,225 --> 00:26:36,705
How do you know my name?

366
00:26:36,785 --> 00:26:39,785
Mr. Xie, you don't allow me
to dispatch new generals.

367
00:26:40,665 --> 00:26:42,425
And you seem to have decent excuses.

368
00:26:43,265 --> 00:26:45,945
Actually, it's just because
they are not loyal to you.

369
00:26:46,545 --> 00:26:47,745
Then do you think

370
00:26:48,665 --> 00:26:52,705
you can plant your own men
after you stop me?

371
00:26:53,305 --> 00:26:54,945
You don't trust me.

372
00:26:56,385 --> 00:26:58,105
I don't trust you either.

373
00:26:59,145 --> 00:27:00,985
So we should place our trust in Chu Ling.

374
00:27:02,025 --> 00:27:04,665
We must believe he will handle
everything before he dies.

375
00:27:05,345 --> 00:27:06,665
Chaos won't occur.

376
00:27:07,185 --> 00:27:09,425
Northern Desert foes won't invade.

377
00:27:11,145 --> 00:27:14,225
Once our state is in crisis,
we'll be in danger.

378
00:27:14,825 --> 00:27:16,305
So will Chu Ling.

379
00:27:17,145 --> 00:27:18,145
If our state falls,

380
00:27:18,225 --> 00:27:20,905
as the Grand Princess,
her daughter will die too.

381
00:27:20,985 --> 00:27:25,585
Chu Ling won't let her daughter
fall into danger.

382
00:27:30,665 --> 00:27:31,545
Fine.

383
00:27:33,185 --> 00:27:36,145
Since the generals can't go to Yunzhong,

384
00:27:37,025 --> 00:27:38,185
Mr. Xie,

385
00:27:40,825 --> 00:27:45,345
your private troops must not go there too.

386
00:27:51,705 --> 00:27:55,025
I read the files on your father's
connection to the Third Prince.

387
00:27:59,265 --> 00:28:00,185
Who are you?

388
00:28:02,665 --> 00:28:04,025
The Third Prince was executed.

389
00:28:04,105 --> 00:28:05,305
His subordinates were demoted.

390
00:28:06,065 --> 00:28:07,545
Your family collapsed.

391
00:28:07,625 --> 00:28:09,665
You became a patrol soldier then.

392
00:28:09,745 --> 00:28:12,465
Would you really waste your life
in the middle of nowhere?

393
00:28:14,305 --> 00:28:16,585
-Who on earth are you?
-I'm here to help.

394
00:28:17,945 --> 00:28:18,905
We're merely bandits

395
00:28:18,985 --> 00:28:20,985
who have fled from Cangmu Stronghold.

396
00:28:21,905 --> 00:28:24,305
You patrolled here and ran into bandits.

397
00:28:24,385 --> 00:28:27,105
If you take us back,
you'll make great merit.

398
00:28:27,185 --> 00:28:28,865
We just switched allegiance.

399
00:28:28,945 --> 00:28:30,225
Don't be suspicious.

400
00:28:30,825 --> 00:28:35,705
You just need to decide
whether you want that credit.

401
00:28:36,585 --> 00:28:39,585
Back in Wangcheng,
if you dare to play tricks,

402
00:28:40,105 --> 00:28:41,145
I'll kill you immediately.

403
00:28:41,225 --> 00:28:43,705
Since you accept this merit,

404
00:28:43,785 --> 00:28:46,265
we will behave ourselves.

405
00:28:49,665 --> 00:28:51,465
CHARTING THE COSMOS

406
00:28:51,545 --> 00:28:52,385
Mr. Xie,

407
00:28:54,865 --> 00:28:59,225
where is your brother
planning to take the Grand Princess?

408
00:29:03,625 --> 00:29:05,705
My brother has been suspended.

409
00:29:06,305 --> 00:29:07,745
Her Highness is recuperating.

410
00:29:08,345 --> 00:29:09,785
I don't know what you mean.

411
00:29:10,465 --> 00:29:12,185
Then let me remind you.

412
00:29:12,905 --> 00:29:15,505
He who holds the emperor
commands the lords.

413
00:29:15,585 --> 00:29:17,225
But he who holds the Grand Princess

414
00:29:17,865 --> 00:29:20,265
only commands Chu Ling.

415
00:29:20,345 --> 00:29:22,985
It's a bad bargain.
You know that perfectly well.

416
00:29:23,065 --> 00:29:25,145
Then you should also know.

417
00:29:26,745 --> 00:29:28,585
Chu Zhao must not die.

418
00:29:29,385 --> 00:29:31,625
She must stay alive.

419
00:29:31,705 --> 00:29:35,985
Only when she's alive
will the court avoid another rebellion.

420
00:29:36,505 --> 00:29:40,425
Then our game can keep going, right?

421
00:29:41,145 --> 00:29:42,505
In that case,

422
00:29:43,185 --> 00:29:45,745
hope your ninth brother
will protect Her Highness well

423
00:29:47,265 --> 00:29:49,825
as we all expect him to.

424
00:29:53,345 --> 00:29:55,145
Of course.

425
00:29:58,545 --> 00:30:00,665
But you're wrong about one thing.

426
00:30:02,505 --> 00:30:04,785
My brother didn't take away
the Grand Princess.

427
00:30:05,385 --> 00:30:08,905
Instead, the Grand Princess
took away my brother.

428
00:30:11,625 --> 00:30:15,505
CHARTING THE COSMOS

429
00:30:16,665 --> 00:30:18,465
Mr. Deng, you're pretty bold.

430
00:30:22,145 --> 00:30:25,065
You removed the coffin
bestowed by Her Highness.

431
00:30:26,025 --> 00:30:28,625
Her Highness withdrew from the court.

432
00:30:28,705 --> 00:30:30,225
Why can't I move this little thing then?

433
00:30:44,465 --> 00:30:45,745
Impressive.

434
00:30:45,825 --> 00:30:46,745
Let me try.

435
00:30:53,425 --> 00:30:55,425
Hello, Miss Qi. Hello, Lady Tang.

436
00:31:01,985 --> 00:31:03,665
That totally ruined my mood.

437
00:31:04,465 --> 00:31:05,665
What are you talking about?

438
00:31:05,745 --> 00:31:06,785
What did we do?

439
00:31:06,865 --> 00:31:10,025
Is it because we didn't bow
to Miss Chu Tang?

440
00:31:10,705 --> 00:31:12,025
You should be straightforward.

441
00:31:12,625 --> 00:31:14,545
Why do you bother to be so sarcastic?

442
00:31:15,145 --> 00:31:16,185
All right.

443
00:31:18,865 --> 00:31:21,705
Lady Tang, let me ask you.

444
00:31:21,785 --> 00:31:25,705
Do you know if your uncle General Chu Ling
fails to defend the frontier,

445
00:31:25,785 --> 00:31:27,825
people will suffer?

446
00:31:32,105 --> 00:31:33,465
I know.

447
00:31:33,545 --> 00:31:34,705
You speak recklessly

448
00:31:35,305 --> 00:31:37,385
because you worry
about our state and people.

449
00:31:37,465 --> 00:31:38,545
This is good.

450
00:31:39,065 --> 00:31:41,345
Unmarried ladies like us
should pay more attention

451
00:31:41,425 --> 00:31:42,545
to state affairs.

452
00:31:42,625 --> 00:31:46,145
Only then will we know about the hardships
of our state and people.

453
00:31:46,825 --> 00:31:49,225
However, we must not judge by appearances

454
00:31:49,305 --> 00:31:51,385
or take a part for the whole.

455
00:31:51,465 --> 00:31:53,185
We didn't speak recklessly.

456
00:31:53,265 --> 00:31:55,145
What we said is the truth.

457
00:31:55,225 --> 00:31:56,865
What is truth? What you see is truth.

458
00:31:56,945 --> 00:31:58,265
Did you see with your own eyes

459
00:31:58,345 --> 00:32:01,425
that my uncle failed
and our foes gained an advantage?

460
00:32:02,025 --> 00:32:03,065
Don't try to deny it.

461
00:32:06,185 --> 00:32:07,745
Do you know how big Yunzhong is?

462
00:32:07,825 --> 00:32:10,305
Do you know how many soldiers
are involved in a battle?

463
00:32:10,385 --> 00:32:13,505
Do you know how many people
from the Northern Desert

464
00:32:13,585 --> 00:32:16,865
have come to travel
on the trade routes of our state?

465
00:32:17,585 --> 00:32:22,385
When the case is investigated,
my uncle will be convicted or vindicated.

466
00:32:22,985 --> 00:32:26,305
But now,
no one can convict him without proof.

467
00:32:28,465 --> 00:32:31,865
Once war breaks out,
situations are volatile and intricate.

468
00:32:32,385 --> 00:32:34,905
Even the Emperor's orders
aren't always followed.

469
00:32:35,665 --> 00:32:38,945
And you don't even know
what exactly happened in Yunzhong.

470
00:32:39,025 --> 00:32:40,385
How can you parrot what others say?

471
00:32:41,385 --> 00:32:42,305
Let's go.

472
00:32:44,465 --> 00:32:45,305
LOTUS PAVILION

473
00:32:45,385 --> 00:32:46,425
Come on.

474
00:32:47,705 --> 00:32:48,545
Tang.

475
00:32:49,185 --> 00:32:50,225
I…

476
00:32:55,145 --> 00:32:56,385
I'm sorry.

477
00:32:56,465 --> 00:32:58,225
Miss Chu, you seem to be in good spirits.

478
00:32:59,385 --> 00:33:01,385
Your family is in turmoil.

479
00:33:01,465 --> 00:33:02,545
But you're in the mood for tea.

480
00:33:03,705 --> 00:33:06,145
If you're here for some fun, get in there.

481
00:33:06,225 --> 00:33:07,505
More fun with the storyteller.

482
00:33:08,105 --> 00:33:10,145
Tang, how can you be so rude to Mr. Deng?

483
00:33:11,265 --> 00:33:12,625
He wanted to watch the fun,

484
00:33:12,705 --> 00:33:14,825
then I recommended the opera house.
How was that rude?

485
00:33:14,905 --> 00:33:17,065
Has my entire family
already been convicted

486
00:33:17,145 --> 00:33:18,185
that I can't even speak?

487
00:33:18,265 --> 00:33:19,265
You can speak.

488
00:33:19,865 --> 00:33:22,745
Lady Tang, your frankness
is quite admirable.

489
00:33:23,345 --> 00:33:24,985
Even if your uncle ends up guilty,

490
00:33:25,065 --> 00:33:26,745
the Grand Princess will stand by you.

491
00:33:28,865 --> 00:33:31,065
You've got a point there,
Mr. Deng. Farewell.

492
00:33:35,225 --> 00:33:37,025
Tang, wait for me.

493
00:33:43,265 --> 00:33:44,425
Oh no.

494
00:33:44,505 --> 00:33:46,705
What was I even saying?

495
00:33:46,785 --> 00:33:47,705
Yeah.

496
00:33:48,225 --> 00:33:49,385
Scared now, huh?

497
00:33:50,145 --> 00:33:51,865
What happened to all that swagger?

498
00:33:53,025 --> 00:33:55,265
Come on. Don't tease me.

499
00:33:55,345 --> 00:33:58,225
Just now, I lost my temper.

500
00:33:58,305 --> 00:34:00,625
I couldn't remember what I said or did.

501
00:34:02,505 --> 00:34:03,625
Now I've come to my senses.

502
00:34:05,305 --> 00:34:06,705
I'm so terrified.

503
00:34:12,025 --> 00:34:13,465
Anyway, what's gone is gone.

504
00:34:13,985 --> 00:34:17,025
Even if I said that,
who would dare to do anything?

505
00:34:17,985 --> 00:34:19,145
Tang,

506
00:34:20,465 --> 00:34:22,784
you've changed.

507
00:34:25,025 --> 00:34:26,705
You never argued with anyone before.

508
00:34:27,425 --> 00:34:29,585
Not to mention arguing
for General Chu and Chu Zhao.

509
00:34:34,185 --> 00:34:35,665
Oh, my uncle.

510
00:34:36,385 --> 00:34:38,065
Please don't get convicted.

511
00:34:39,465 --> 00:34:40,505
And Zhao…

512
00:34:40,585 --> 00:34:42,264
Come back early.

513
00:34:42,865 --> 00:34:45,264
‎WANGCHENG OUTSKIRTS

514
00:34:50,225 --> 00:34:54,304
Before fully recovering,
you exhausted yourself again.

515
00:34:54,824 --> 00:34:55,824
I know what I'm doing.

516
00:34:59,385 --> 00:35:00,465
Can we trust this man?

517
00:35:01,065 --> 00:35:04,585
Liang Qiang is low-ranking,
but he's a regular soldier.

518
00:35:04,665 --> 00:35:07,105
Xiao Xun's troops
won't provoke or inspect him.

519
00:35:07,745 --> 00:35:10,905
In this way,
we'll be able to avoid Xiao Xun's spies.

520
00:35:11,505 --> 00:35:14,425
Besides, we're taking a carriage now.

521
00:35:14,505 --> 00:35:16,345
No soft cushions or pillows.

522
00:35:16,425 --> 00:35:19,065
But at least, we don't need to trek.

523
00:35:19,145 --> 00:35:21,065
How nice. Two birds, one stone.

524
00:35:25,025 --> 00:35:29,865
WANGCHENG

525
00:35:37,225 --> 00:35:38,145
Get them down.

526
00:36:07,625 --> 00:36:08,665
The ruts are weird.

527
00:36:09,265 --> 00:36:11,145
It seems to be a straw cart
heading for town.

528
00:36:13,345 --> 00:36:14,905
The straw binding is loose.

529
00:36:15,905 --> 00:36:17,185
Usually, a loosely bound cart bears

530
00:36:17,785 --> 00:36:20,105
no more than three to five hundred jin.

531
00:36:20,185 --> 00:36:22,585
But the ruts are deeper
than half a finger.

532
00:36:22,665 --> 00:36:24,065
It carries at least

533
00:36:25,305 --> 00:36:26,505
800 jin.

534
00:36:26,585 --> 00:36:28,025
There's something else in the cart.

535
00:36:31,705 --> 00:36:32,865
Judging from the ruts,

536
00:36:32,945 --> 00:36:36,785
no fewer than ten carts
have entered town today.

537
00:36:37,465 --> 00:36:41,025
Someone's taking so much trouble
to do something to this town.

538
00:36:41,625 --> 00:36:43,225
This is a strategic frontier town.

539
00:36:43,745 --> 00:36:48,145
If it falls, Yunzhong Prefecture
will be attacked from the front and rear.

540
00:36:49,785 --> 00:36:51,825
Xiao Xun sent his men in disguise.

541
00:36:52,665 --> 00:36:55,025
But the gate guards should have inspected

542
00:36:55,105 --> 00:36:56,985
either disguised men or hidden weapons.

543
00:36:57,065 --> 00:36:58,505
By Article ten of the Frontier Code,

544
00:36:59,145 --> 00:37:02,865
a Military Supply Token will exempt
all goods from inspection.

545
00:37:03,705 --> 00:37:05,945
Given Xiao Xun's status,
getting some tokens

546
00:37:06,945 --> 00:37:07,945
would be quite easy.

547
00:37:09,665 --> 00:37:10,505
Follow me in.

548
00:37:11,665 --> 00:37:12,745
You go back now.

549
00:37:14,345 --> 00:37:15,625
Keep up.

550
00:37:21,665 --> 00:37:22,825
Your Highness,

551
00:37:22,905 --> 00:37:25,185
3,000 elite troops of Northern Desert
passed Xinggu Pass

552
00:37:25,265 --> 00:37:26,905
and reached Shalang Col,
less than 100 li from Wangcheng.

553
00:37:28,945 --> 00:37:30,665
Tell them to go along the official road

554
00:37:31,905 --> 00:37:33,825
with the travel permit,
disguised as caravans.

555
00:37:34,465 --> 00:37:37,625
-Make sure they're well provisioned.
-Yes.

556
00:37:38,225 --> 00:37:40,105
We won't dispatch troops

557
00:37:41,305 --> 00:37:42,625
until they take Wangcheng.

558
00:37:44,665 --> 00:37:47,105
Ge. Ge. Bad news.

559
00:37:48,145 --> 00:37:51,105
Our scout spotted
3,000 soldiers headed for Wangcheng

560
00:37:51,185 --> 00:37:52,945
from the official road northwest
toward Xiaonan,

561
00:37:53,025 --> 00:37:54,505
disguised as caravans.

562
00:37:54,585 --> 00:37:56,065
From Xiaonan?

563
00:37:57,425 --> 00:37:59,825
Wangcheng is vital
to the rear of Yunzhong.

564
00:38:00,345 --> 00:38:01,705
Once it falls,

565
00:38:01,785 --> 00:38:04,505
Xiao Xun will block supplies
within half a day.

566
00:38:05,345 --> 00:38:09,505
By then, the Yunzhong troops
will be besieged with no supplies.

567
00:38:10,105 --> 00:38:12,945
Massive soldiers
will be desperately trapped.

568
00:38:14,665 --> 00:38:15,665
Oh no.

569
00:38:16,185 --> 00:38:17,865
At the rate of traveling,

570
00:38:18,785 --> 00:38:20,785
the two of them are just at Wangcheng.

571
00:38:20,865 --> 00:38:23,945
JUSTICE HANGS ON HIGH

572
00:38:24,025 --> 00:38:27,985
General, in Cangmu Forest, I caught
two bandits of Cangmu Stronghold.

573
00:38:28,505 --> 00:38:30,625
Bandits have done countless crimes.

574
00:38:30,705 --> 00:38:31,745
Execute them now.

575
00:38:33,545 --> 00:38:35,465
General, it's easy for you to kill us.

576
00:38:35,545 --> 00:38:38,185
But I wonder if you can remain so decisive

577
00:38:38,265 --> 00:38:40,145
when northern foes break into town.

578
00:38:46,265 --> 00:38:48,665
How dare you!

579
00:38:48,745 --> 00:38:50,545
How could you spread a fallacy here?

580
00:38:50,625 --> 00:38:53,465
If we were real bandits,
why would we come voluntarily?

581
00:38:54,465 --> 00:38:57,345
As we entered town,
we spotted enemy spies in disguise.

582
00:38:57,945 --> 00:39:00,385
The ruts of straw carts
are abnormally deep.

583
00:39:00,465 --> 00:39:01,465
Weapons must be hidden there.

584
00:39:02,145 --> 00:39:04,665
Now, instead of executing me,

585
00:39:04,745 --> 00:39:07,705
you should send men
to close the city gate,

586
00:39:07,785 --> 00:39:09,425
search the city, and increase security.

587
00:39:09,505 --> 00:39:10,465
Shut up!

588
00:39:13,225 --> 00:39:15,825
How dare a bandit
comment on military affairs,

589
00:39:15,905 --> 00:39:18,145
stir up unrest, and shake troop morale?

590
00:39:18,225 --> 00:39:20,225
I'll chop your heads off now

591
00:39:20,305 --> 00:39:22,425
and hang them
on the city wall as a warning!

592
00:39:22,505 --> 00:39:24,105
Kill them!

593
00:39:37,225 --> 00:39:38,345
Brilliant plan.

594
00:39:38,425 --> 00:39:40,185
Xiao Xun didn't kill you.

595
00:39:40,265 --> 00:39:42,225
But someone on your own side will.

596
00:39:42,305 --> 00:39:43,225
You're wrong.

597
00:39:43,745 --> 00:39:47,065
You've been the only one on my own side.

598
00:39:48,945 --> 00:39:50,505
Outrageous. Outrageous!

599
00:39:50,585 --> 00:39:53,145
Seize them immediately and execute them!

600
00:39:53,945 --> 00:39:54,785
Don't you dare!

601
00:40:02,705 --> 00:40:04,825
Zhong Changrong,
deputy of the Guard General,

602
00:40:04,905 --> 00:40:06,665
is here to see the Grand Princess!

603
00:40:43,705 --> 00:40:44,545
Hey, girl.

604
00:40:46,785 --> 00:40:47,625
Girl.

605
00:41:15,065 --> 00:41:16,025
Hey.

606
00:41:19,345 --> 00:41:20,225
Hey.

607
00:41:20,945 --> 00:41:22,025
It's been years.

608
00:41:22,665 --> 00:41:23,905
Don't you recognize me?

609
00:41:27,585 --> 00:41:28,505
Mr. Zhong.

610
00:41:29,145 --> 00:41:31,025
Did anyone bully you?

611
00:41:35,265 --> 00:41:36,105
You…

612
00:41:36,625 --> 00:41:38,785
You vile creature! Are you blind?

613
00:41:38,865 --> 00:41:41,745
This is General Chu's daughter,
the Grand Princess.

614
00:41:42,425 --> 00:41:43,625
Just now,

615
00:41:43,705 --> 00:41:45,985
who were you going to execute?

616
00:41:48,745 --> 00:41:50,265
Sorry, I misjudged you.

617
00:41:50,345 --> 00:41:51,745
Mercy, Your Highness.

618
00:41:53,745 --> 00:41:54,585
My eyes failed me,

619
00:41:55,185 --> 00:41:56,665
and I offended Your Highness.

620
00:41:56,745 --> 00:41:57,585
Please forgive me.

621
00:41:58,825 --> 00:41:59,825
Not your fault.

622
00:42:00,625 --> 00:42:03,545
Your priority is to close the city gate
and defend deep.

623
00:42:03,625 --> 00:42:06,025
Find out Northern Desert foes and weapons.

624
00:42:07,305 --> 00:42:09,185
I swear to hold the city.

625
00:42:10,585 --> 00:42:13,945
Mr. Zhao,
your official headwear is still yours now.

626
00:42:14,665 --> 00:42:19,105
But if this city falls,
you will lose it and your life.

627
00:42:19,705 --> 00:42:22,185
I swear to stand and fall with the city!

628
00:42:22,785 --> 00:42:24,825
Leave us right now. Get to work.

629
00:42:31,545 --> 00:42:33,425
Mr. Zhong, why are you here?

630
00:42:35,265 --> 00:42:36,665
Your father was worried about you,

631
00:42:36,745 --> 00:42:39,065
so he sent me here
to get you back to Yunzhong.

632
00:42:39,145 --> 00:42:40,865
When I was halfway,

633
00:42:40,945 --> 00:42:42,745
I got this man's message,

634
00:42:42,825 --> 00:42:44,865
saying you would reach Wangcheng.

635
00:42:45,465 --> 00:42:47,025
I traveled hundreds of li for nothing

636
00:42:47,105 --> 00:42:49,265
and rushed back immediately.

637
00:42:49,345 --> 00:42:50,905
You arrived later than I expected.

638
00:42:51,505 --> 00:42:54,145
Zhong, you should work on your speed.

639
00:42:55,265 --> 00:42:57,025
How rude. Nonsense.

640
00:42:58,945 --> 00:43:00,505
Report!

641
00:43:00,585 --> 00:43:01,665
‎THE WAY OF HEAVEN, THE JUSTICE OF ALL

642
00:43:01,745 --> 00:43:03,145
Scouts have spotted

643
00:43:03,225 --> 00:43:05,305
3,000 enemy troops came from the north.

644
00:43:05,385 --> 00:43:07,185
They're within 50 li of this city.

